20%26quot%3BSevere%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20national%20capital%20continues%20to%20grapple%20with%20toxic%20air%20quality.%20According%20to%20the%20Central%20Pollution%20Control%20Board%20(CPCB)%2C%20the%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20recorded%20was%20410%20at%206%20a.m.%20on%20Monday%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20thin%20layer%20of%20fog%20blanketed%20the%20city%2C%20reducing%20visibility%2C%20while%20the%20minimum%20temperature%20dropped%20to%209.2%20degrees%20Celsius%20at%205%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20according%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD).%20A%20cloudy%20sky%20with%20light%20rain%20was%20experienced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20emerged%20which%20showed%20people%20taking%20refuge%20in%20the%20night%20shelter%20homes%20located%20at%20Lodhi%20Road%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20the%20harsh%20winters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20temperatures%20have%20dropped%20here%20because%20it%20has%20been%20raining...%20the%20rain%20started%20around%205%20am%20today..%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20local.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20areas%20in%20Delhi%20reported%20alarming%20AQI%20levels%2C%20including%20Wazirpur%20(464)%2C%20Ashok%20Vihar%20(460)%2C%20Mundka%20(446)%2C%20Burari%20Crossing%20(445)%2C%20and%20Anand%20Vihar%20(443).%20Notably%2C%20air%20quality%20in%20Dwarka-Sector%208%20(393)%20and%20Najafgarh%20(372)%20hovered%20just%20below%20the%20%E2%80%98severe'%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20PM2.5%20levels%20(Particulate%20Matter)%2C%20a%20major%20pollutant%2C%20remained%20dangerously%20high%2C%20with%2037%20out%20of%2039%20monitoring%20stations%20recording%20%E2%80%98severe%20plus'%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%202.5%20particles%2C%20small%20enough%20to%20penetrate%20deep%20into%20the%20lungs%2C%20pose%20severe%20health%20risks%2C%20particularly%20for%20vulnerable%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20worsening%20pollution%2C%20the%20Graded%20Response%20Action%20Plan%20(GRAP)%20Stage%20IV%20measures%20have%20been%20enforced%20across%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20since%20December%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20emergency%20steps%20aim%20to%20curb%20pollution%20but%20have%20had%20limited%20immediate%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20recently%20directed%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Haryana%20to%20impose%20firecracker%20bans%20akin%20to%20Delhi's%20and%20emphasised%20stringent%20implementation%20of%20GRAP%20and%20the%20Solid%20Waste%20Management%20Rules%2C%202016.%20The%20apex%20court%20also%20ordered%20NCR%20states%20to%20deploy%20teams%20at%20Delhi's%20entry%20points%20to%20monitor%20compliance%20with%20GRAP%20IV%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResidents%20are%20increasingly%20reporting%20health%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20pollution%2C%20including%20respiratory%20problems%20and%20eye%20irritation.%20The%20combination%20of%20thick%20fog%2C%20and%20toxic%20air%20has%20made%20life%20challenging%20for%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%20with%20many%20calling%20for%20stronger%20and%20more%20effective%20measures%20to%20combat%20the%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734920460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fgkauqq5g_delhi-pollution-_625x300_23_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhi-reels-under-severe-air-quality-fog-and-cold-wave-7311324%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Monday%20morning%2C%20at%206am%2C%20Delhi%20recorded%20410%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%2C%20falling%20under%20the%20'severe'%20category.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-air-pollution-delhi-reels-under-severe-air-quality-fog-and-cold-wave-73113