ansgender%20lunacy%26quot%3B%20on%20day%20one%20of%20his%20presidency%2C%20as%20Republicans%20--%20set%20to%20control%20both%20chambers%20of%20Congress%20and%20the%20White%20House%20--%20continue%20their%20push%20against%20LGBTQ%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20sign%20executive%20orders%20to%20end%20child%20sexual%20mutilation%2C%20get%20transgender%20out%20of%20the%20military%20and%20out%20of%20our%20elementary%20schools%20and%20middle%20schools%20and%20high%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20president-elect%20said%20at%20an%20event%20for%20young%20conservatives%20in%20Phoenix%2C%20Arizona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20vowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bkeep%20men%20out%20of%20women's%20sports%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20will%20be%20the%20official%20policy%20of%20the%20United%20States%20government%20that%20there%20are%20only%20two%20genders%2C%20male%20and%20female.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20AmericaFest%20conference%20in%20a%20border%20state%20he%20easily%20carried%20in%20the%20November%20election%2C%20Trump%20further%20promised%20immediate%20measures%20against%20%26quot%3Bmigrant%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20vowed%20to%20designate%20drug%20cartels%20as%20foreign%20terrorist%20organizations%2C%20and%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20talk%20of%20restoring%20US%20control%20of%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransgender%20issues%20have%20roiled%20US%20politics%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20as%20Democratic-%20and%20Republican-controlled%20states%20have%20moved%20in%20opposite%20directions%20on%20policy%20such%20as%20medical%20treatment%20and%20what%20books%20on%20the%20topic%20are%20allowed%20in%20public%20or%20school%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20when%20the%20US%20Congress%20approved%20its%20annual%20defense%20budget%2C%20it%20included%20a%20provision%20to%20block%20funding%20of%20some%20gender-affirming%20care%20for%20the%20transgender%20children%20of%20service%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%20Sunday%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%20something%20of%20a%20victory%20lap%2C%20Trump%20made%20expansive%20promises%20for%20his%20second%20term%20--%20and%20drew%20a%20dark%20picture%20of%20the%20four%20years%20preceding%20it%2C%20under%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20and%20Vice%20President%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20the%20latter%20of%20whom%20he%20defeated%20in%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20January%2020%2C%20the%20United%20States%20will%20turn%20the%20page%20forever%20on%20four%20long%2C%20horrible%20years%20of%20failure%2C%20incompetence%2C%20national%20decline%2C%20and%20we%20will%20inaugurate%20a%20new%20era%20of%20peace%2C%20prosperity%20and%20national%20greatness%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20swearing-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20I%20will%20stop%20the%20chaos%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20I%20will%20prevent%2C%20I%20promise%2C%20World%20War%20III.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20golden%20age%20of%20America%20is%20upon%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20president-elect%20has%20yet%20to%20explain%20publicly%20how%20he%20plans%20to%20bring%20a%20quick%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20or%20to%20bring%20peace%20to%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20sort%20of%20bellicose%20language%20he%20sometimes%20used%20even%20against%20US%20allies%20in%20the%20past%2C%20Trump%20said%20Sunday%20that%20Panamanian%20authorities%20%26quot%3Bhaven't%20treated%20us%20fairly%26quot%3B%20in%20their%20operation%20of%20the%20Panama%20Canal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20said%20earlier%20that%20fees%20for%20use%20of%20the%20canal%20--%20construction%20of%20which%20was%20begun%20by%20France%20and%20completed%20by%20the%20United%20States%20--%20are%20%26quot%3Bridiculous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20added%20Sunday%20that%20if%20the%20principles%20behind%20the%201970s%20treaty%20that%20gav