e%20Lively%20filed%20a%20legal%20complaint%20against%20her%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20with%20Us%26quot%3B%20costar%2C%20Justin%20Baldoni.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETaylor%20Swift%20and%20Hailey%20Bieber%20appeared%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELively's%20complaint%20said%20Baldoni%20and%20his%20team%20conspired%20to%20damage%20her%20reputation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20legal%20complaint%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblake-lively-sues-it-ends-with-us-costar-justin-baldoni-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlake%20Lively%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20that%20her%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20with%20Us%26quot%3B%20costar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjustin-baldoni-blake-lively-drama-it-ends-with-us-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJustin%20Baldoni%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20also%20directed%20and%20produced%20the%20film%2C%20conspired%20to%20damage%20her%20reputation%20and%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20mentions%20Taylor%20Swift%20and%20Hailey%20Bieber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELively%20named%20Baldoni%20and%20six%20other%20defendants%20in%20her%20complaint%2C%20including%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20of%20his%20production%20studio%2C%20Wayfarer%20Studios.%20She%20also%20named%20communications%20crisis%20manager%20Melissa%20Nathan%20of%20The%20Agency%20Group%20PR%20and%20Baldoni's%20publicist%2C%20Jennifer%20Abel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%2C%20Lively%20said%20Baldoni%20and%20his%20team%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bmulti-tiered%20plan%26quot%3B%20using%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20manipulation%26quot%3B%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblake-lively-lawsuit-against-justin-baldoni-5-bombshells-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bdestroy%26quot%3B%20her%20reputation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20plan%20went%20well%20beyond%20standard%20crisis%20PR.%20What%20Ms.%20Nathan%20proposed%20included%20a%20practice%20known%20as%20'Astroturfing%2C'%20which%20has%20been%20defined%20as%20'the%20practice%20of%20publishing%20opinions%20or%20comments%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20in%20the%20media%2C%20etc.%20that%20appear%20to%20come%20from%20ordinary%20members%20of%20the%20public%20but%20actually%20come%20from%20a%20particular%20company%20or%20political%20group%2C'%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20that%20Baldoni%20and%20his%20team%20discussed%20controversies%20around%20Swift%20and%20Bieber%20as%20strategic%20suggestions%20while%20conspiring%20against%20Lively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Freedman%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20Baldoni%20and%20Wayfarer%20Studios%2C%20said%20Lively's%20complaint%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bdesperate%20attempt%20to%20'fix'%20her%20negative%20reputation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0ad43ad-84c4-4bbe-8eea-8c026f4110e6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBaldoni%20and%20his%20team%20considered%20leveraging%20backlash%20around%20Swift%20and%20the%20'weaponization%20of%20feminism%2C'%20the%20complaint%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225633%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taylor%20Swift%20playing%20the%20piano%20during%20a%20performance%20on%20The%20Eras%20Tour.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b9720a955b01c3294d8f77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlake%20Lively's%20complaint%20included%20a%20reference%20to%20Taylor%20Swift.%3Cp%3EAndreas%20Rentz%2FTAS24%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENathan's%20communications%20company%20shared%20a%20%26quot%3BScenario%20Planning%26quot%3B%20document%20with%20Baldoni%20and%20others%20that%20outlined%20potential%20strategies%20%26quot%3Bshould%20%5BMs.%20Lively%5D%20and%20her%20team%20make%20her%20grievances%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20includes%20a%20copy%20of%20that%20document%2C%20which%20Lively's%20attorneys%20obtained%20through%20a%20civil%20subpoena.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20planning%20document%20discussed%20what%20Baldoni's%20team%20could%20do%20if%20Lively's%20husband%2C%20actor%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20publicly%20defended%20her%20against%20critics.%20It%20included%20a%20reference%20to%20Swift%2C%20who%20is%20a%20friend%20of%20Lively.%20The%20pair%20have%20attended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-travis-kelce-chiefs-games-photos-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKansas%20City%20Chiefs%20football%20games%3C%2Fa%3E%20together%20and%20have%20been%20photographed%20by%20paparazzi%20while%20hanging%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20this%2C%20our%20team%20can%20also%20explore%20planting%20stories%20about%20the%20weaponization%20of%20feminism%20and%20how%20people%20in%20BL's%20circle%2C%20like%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20utilizing%20these%20tactics%20to%20'bully'%20into%20getting%20what%20they%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20planning%20document%20says%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2206e5d1b2-81ae-4f0a-9ea4-5a9d20cf3a93%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20Baldoni%20used%20a%20social%20media%20post%20about%20Bieber%20and%20bullying%20as%20an%20example%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hailey%20Bieber%20wearing%20a%20beige%20colored%20long-sleeved%20gown.%20it%20cinches%20over%20her%20stomach%2C%20with%20the%20sides%20exposing%20her%20waist.%20her%20hair%20is%20styled%20loose%20and%20down%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676878e4a3e82c791203eb85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222850%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlake%20Lively's%20complaint%20alluded%20to%20Hailey%20Bieber.%3Cp%3EKarwai%20Tang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELively's%20complaint%20also%20contained%20screenshots%20of%20text%20message%20conversations%20between%20Baldoni%20and%20his%20team%2C%20which%20were%20also%20obtained%20through%20a%20civil%20subpoena.%20According%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20Baldoni%20sent%20a%20text%20message%20to%20his%20publicist%2C%20Abel%2C%20in%20early%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20on%20August%205%2C%202024%2C%20Mr.%20Baldoni%20set%20the%20narrative%20for%20the%20social%20media%20campaign%2C%20sending%20Ms.%20Abel%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20thread%20on%20X%20that%20had%20accused%20another%20female%20celebrity%20of%20bullying%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Baldoni%20stated%2C%20'this%20is%20what%20we%20would%20need.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20media%20post%20included%20two%20pictures%20of%20Bieber%20and%20insinuated%20she%20had%20bullied%20other%20women.%20That%20narrative%20gained%20traction%20on%20social%20media%20in%202023%20and%20resulted%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhailey-bieber-vile-internet-narrative-selena-gomez-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewidespread%20backlash%20against%20Bieber%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Lively%20referred%20Business%20Insider%20to%20a%20statement%20she%20shared%20with%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20that%20my%20legal%20action%20helps%20pull%20back%20the%20curtain%20on%20these%20sinister%20retaliatory%20tactics%20to%20harm%20people%20who%20speak%20up%20about%20misconduct%20and%20helps%20protect%20others%20who%20may%20be%20targeted%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELively%20also%20said%20neither%20she%20nor%20her%20representatives%20planted%20negative%20stories%20about%20Baldoni%20or%20Wayfarer%20Studios.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaldoni's%20attorney%20said%20the%20accusations%20in%20Lively's%20complaint%20were%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20false%2C%20outrageous%20and%20intentionally%20salacious%20with%20an%20intent%20to%20publicly%20hurt%20and%20rehash