Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Kuwait%20News%20Agency%20(KUNA)%20on%20Saturday%2C%20PM%20Modi%20also%20reaffirmed%20India's%20role%20in%20addressing%20global%20challenges%20such%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20food%20and%20energy%20security%20and%20advocating%20for%20the%20Global%20South.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20was%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20the%20Gulf%20nation%20of%20Kuwait%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20Sheikh%20Meshal%20Al-Ahmad%20Al-Jaber%20Al-Sabah%2C%20the%20Emir%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Kuwait.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20Kuwait%20in%2043%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20about%20how%20India's%20soft%20power%20can%20influence%20its%20global%20outreach%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20India's%20civilisational%20ethos%20and%20heritage%20form%20the%20foundation%20of%20its%20soft%20power%2C%20KUNA%20reported.%20PM%20Modi%20further%20asserted%20that%20India's%20soft%20power%20has%20grown%20significantly%20alongside%20its%20expanding%20global%20presence%2C%20particularly%20over%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Kuwait%20and%20the%20Gulf%2C%20Indian%20movies%20stand%20out%20as%20a%20prime%20example%20of%20this%20cultural%20connection.%20We%20have%20seen%20that%20people%20in%20Kuwait%20have%20a%20special%20liking%20for%20Indian%20cinema.%20I%20am%20told%20that%20there%20are%20three%20weekly%20shows%20on%20Kuwait%20Television%20on%20Indian%20movies%20and%20actors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSimilarly%2C%20we%20share%20several%20attributes%20in%20our%20cuisine%20and%20culinary%20traditions.%20Centuries%20of%20people-to-people%20contact%20have%20also%20resulted%20in%20linguistic%20similarities%20and%20shared%20vocabulary.%20India's%20diversity%20and%20emphasis%20on%20peace%2C%20tolerance%20and%20coexistence%20resonate%20with%20the%20values%20of%20Kuwait's%20multicultural%20society.%20Recently%2C%20a%20Kuwaiti%20scholar%20translated%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%20in%20Arabic%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20tourism%20sector%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia's%20tourism%20sector%20offers%20another%20dimension%20of%20soft%20power.%20With%2043%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20sites%2C%20coupled%20with%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20enhance%20visitor%20facilities%2C%20India%20provides%20a%20unique%20blend%20of%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20natural%20beauty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20society%20like%20Kuwait%2C%20with%20which%20India%20shares%20a%20rich%20historical%20connection%2C%20India's%20tourism%20opportunities%20are%20an%20invitation%20to%20explore%20and%20deepen%20the%20shared%20cultural%20ties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Indians%20in%20Kuwait%20have%20contributed%20immensely%20to%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%20as%20doctors%2C%20businessmen%2C%20construction%20workers%2C%20engineers%2C%20nurses%20and%20other%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20we%20elevate%20the%20level%20of%20our%20relationship%20with%20Kuwait%20to%20a%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20I%20believe%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Indian%20community%20will%20only%20grow%20in%20importance.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20Kuwaiti%20authorities%20recognise%20the%20immense%20contributions%20of%20this%20vibrant%20community%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20encouragement%20and%20support%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Kuwaiti-Indian%20energy%20relations%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20energy%20is%20an%20important%20pillar%20of%20the%20bilateral%20partnership%2C%20estimating%20that%20last%20year%2C%20trade%20exchange%20crossed%20USD%2010%20billion%2C%20which%20reflects%20the%20deep%20trust%20and%20mutual%20benefit%20underpinning%20this%20partnership%2C%20KUNA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20nations%20have%20consistently%20ranked%20among%20the%20top%2010%20trading%20partners%20in%20the%20energy%20sector.%20Indian%20companies%20actively%20engage%20in%20importing%20crude%20oil%2C%20LPG%2C%20and%20petroleum%20products%20from%20Kuwait%20while%20also%20exporting%20petroleum%20products%20to%20Kuwait.%20Currently%2C%20Kuwait%20stands%20as%20India's%206th%20largest%20crude%20supplier%20and%204th%20largest%20LPG%20supplier%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20addition%20to%20conventional%20hydrocarbon%20trade%2C%20there%20exist%20a%20plethora%20of%20new%20areas%20for%20cooperation%2C%20including%20an%20entire%20value%20chain%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%20as%20well%20as%20joint%20efforts%20in%20low-carbon%20solutions%20such%20as%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20biofuels%2C%20and%20carbon%20capture%20technologies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20India's%20global%20role%20as%20a%20voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20PM%20Modi%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20privileged%20to%20speak%20for%20the%20Global%20South.%20We%20share%20much%20in%20common%20with%20our%20fellow%20developing%20countries%20-%20from%20history%20to%20the%20aspirations%20of%20our%20people.%20We%20therefore%20not%20only%20understand%20but%20feel%20their%20concerns.%20The%20ongoing%20conflicts%20and%20the%20resultant%20challenges%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20fertiliser%20have%20hit%20the%20global%20south%20hard.%20They%20are%20also%20disproportionately%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20climate%20change%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20hailed%20his%20country%20as%20a%20reliable%20development%20partner%20for%20the%20global%20south%2C%20a%20first%20responder%20in%20times%20of%20crises%20for%20them%20and%20for%20others%2C%20a%20leader%20on%20climate%20action%20and%20a%20champion%20of%20inclusive%20growth%20and%20development.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20gave%20voice%20to%20the%20concerns%20of%20developing%20countries%20when%20we%20assumed%20the%20Presidency%20of%20the%20G20.%20We%20hosted%20three%20Voice%20of%20the%20Global%20South%20Summits%20to%20amplify%20and%20act%20on%20the%20pressing%20needs%20of%20people.%20We%20were%20honoured%20that%20the%20African%20Union%20became%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20G20%20at%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Summit.%20This%20was%20a%20historic%20achievement%20for%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20and%20a%20proud%20moment%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20regional%20and%20global%20conflicts%2C%20involving%20Gaza%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20PM%20Modi%20emphasised%20that%20solutions%20cannot%20be%20found%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20stressing%20the%20importance%20of%20sincere%20and%20practical%20engagement%20between%20stakeholders%20for%20bridging%20differences%20and%20achieving%20negotiated%20settlements%2C%20KUNA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20highlighted%20that%20India%20recently%20provided%2070%20tons%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20nearly%2065%20tons%20of%20medicines%20to%20Gaza%2C%20along%20with%20contributing%20USD%2010%20million%20to%20UNRWA%20over%20the%20past%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20reaffirmed%20India's%20commitment%20to%20a%20negotiated%20two-state%20solution%20aimed%20at%20establishing%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%2C%20and%20viable%20Palestinian%20state%20with%20secure%20and%20recognised%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20environmental%20sustainability%20initiatives%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20facing%20several%20challenges%2C%20but%20none%20more%20pressing%20than%20climate%20change.%20Our%20planet%20is%20under%20stress.%20We%20need%20urgent%20collective%20action%20and%20one%20that%20involves%20the%20entire%20global%20community.%20No%20one%20can%20do%20it%20alone.%20We%20must%20come%20together.%20India%20wants%20to%20lead%20and%20bring%20all%20countries%20together%20to%20foster%20pro-planet%20action.%20This%20is%20the%20idea%20behind%20our%20championing%20various%20green%20global%20initiatives.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20regarded%20the%20India-led%20green%20initiatives%20as%20platforms%20for%20all%20nations%20to%20collectively%20address%20climate%20change%2C%20promote%20environmental%20sustainability%2C%20build%20disaster-resilient%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20drive%20the%20global%20transition%20towards%20clean%20energy%2C%20KUNA%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20attended%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20of%20the%2026th%20Arabian%20Gulf%20Cup%20in%20Kuwait%20on%20Saturday%20as%20the%20'Guest%20of%20Honour'%20of%20Amir%20Sheikh%20Meshal%20Al-Ahmad%20Al-Jaber%20Al-Sabah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmir%20of%20Kuwait%20and%20Sheikh%20Sabah%20Al-Khaled%20Al-Sabah%20Al-Hamad%20Al-Mubarak%20Al-Sabah%2C%20Crown%20Prince%20of%20Kuwait%20received%20PM%20Modi%20at%20Bayan%20Palace%20on%20Sunday%20and%20was%20accorded%20a%20ceremonial%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20expressed%20his%20deep%20appreciation%20to%20Al-Ahmad%20Al-Jaber%20Al-Sabah%20for%20conferring%20on%20him%20the%20highest%20award%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Kuwait%20'The%20Order%20of%20Mubarak%20Al%20Kabeer.'%20The%20leaders%20exchanged%20views%20on%20bilateral%2C%20global%2C%20regional%20and%20multilateral%20issues%20of%20mutual%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sides%20also%20recalled%20the%20centuries-old%20historical%20ties%20rooted%20in%20shared%20history%20and%20cultural%20affinities.%20They%20noted%20with%20satisfaction%20the%20regular%20interactions%20at%20various%20levels%20which%20have%20helped%20in%20generating%20and%20sustaining%20the%20momentum%20in%20the%20multifaceted%20bilateral%20cooperation.%20Both%20sides%20emphasised%20sustaining%20the%20recent%20momentum%20in%20high-level%20exchanges%20through%20regular%20bilateral%20exchanges%20at%20Ministerial%20and%20senior-official%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20f