26quot%3B%20said%20PCB%20spokesperson%20Amir%20Mir%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20IANS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20has%20formally%20informed%20the%20ICC%20about%20the%20neutral%20venue%20decision.%20Now%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan's%20Champions%20Trophy%20matches%20will%20be%20held%20in%20the%20UAE.%20The%20decision%20regarding%20the%20neutral%20venue%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20was%20to%20be%20made%20by%20the%20host%2C%20Pakistan.%20The%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20venue%20was%20made%20after%20a%20meeting%20between%20Mohsin%20Naqvi%20and%20Sheikh%20Al%20Nahyan.%20Sheikh%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20currently%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20is%20also%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20UAE%20Cricket%20Board%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20board%20of%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20on%20Thursday%20confirmed%20that%20matches%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20in%20upcoming%20ICC%20events%20till%202027%2C%20including%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%20will%20be%20played%20at%20neutral%20venues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20neutral%20venue%20arrangements%20will%20apply%20to%20the%20upcoming%20ICC%20Men's%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20(hosted%20by%20Pakistan)%2C%20set%20to%20be%20played%20in%20February%20and%20March%202025%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202025%20(hosted%20by%20India)%20and%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202026%20(hosted%20by%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka).%20Moreover%2C%20it%20will%20also%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202028%2C%20whose%20hosting%20rights%20have%20been%20awarded%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20strained%20political%20relations%2C%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20only%20compete%20in%20international%20events%20like%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20Asia%20Cup.%20The%20last%20bilateral%20series%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20was%20held%20in%202012-13%2C%20when%20Pakistan%20toured%20India%20for%20a%20five-match%20white-ball%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Champions%20Trophy%20is%20scheduled%20to%20be%20played%20in%20February%20and%20March%202025.%20Meanwhile%2C%20ICC%20said%20the%20schedule%20for%20the%20marquee%20tournament%20will%20be%20confirmed%20in%20the%20coming%20days.%20Pakistan%20are%20the%20defending%20champions%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20having%20defeated%20India%20by%20180%20runs%20in%20the%20final%20at%20The%20Oval%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20teams%20last%20played%20against%20each%20other%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20New%20York%20earlier%20this%20year%20which%20India%20won%20by%20six%20runs%20and%20went%20on%20to%20claim%20their%20second%20silverware%20in%20the%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734887940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F3mcdaeqg_rohit-sharma-babar-azam-afp_625x300_09_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fafter-refusing-to-travel-to-pakistan-india-will-play-champions-trophy-matches-at-this-venue-report-7308817%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20deadlock%20over%20the%20hosting%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%20finally%20ended%20when%20the%20ICC%20announced%20that%20India%20will%20play%20their%20matches%20of%20the%2050-over%20event%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fafter-refusing-to-travel-to-pakistan-india-will-play-champions-trophy-matches-at-this-venue-report-7308817%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hozier%20Brings%20Christmas%20Vibes%20to%20%E2%80%98Saturday%20Night%20Live%E2%80%99%20With%20Emotional%20Performance%20and%20Changed%20Lyrics%2