s%20pudding%20is%20a%20traditional%20British%20dessert%20popular%20during%20the%20holiday%20season.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22christmas%20pudding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ddebbf479d7575b422e3783%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristmas%20pudding.%3Cp%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Christmas%20pudding%20is%20a%20dense%20fruit%20cake%20often%20made%20weeks%20or%20even%20months%20in%20advance.%20This%20time%20allows%20the%20dried%20fruit%20to%20soak%20up%20alcohol%20that's%20regularly%20poured%20onto%20the%20cake%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20it's%20consumed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Christmas%2C%20the%20cake%20is%20set%20alight%20and%20then%20topped%20with%20a%20sauce%20of%20brandy%20butter%20or%20rum%20butter%2C%20cream%2C%20lemon%20cream%2C%20ice%20cream%2C%20custard%2C%20or%20sweetened%20b%C3%A9chamel.%20It%20is%20also%20sometimes%20sprinkled%20with%20caster%20or%20powdered%20sugar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20years%2C%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20even%20gifted%20each%20member%20of%20her%20staff%20a%20Christmas%20pudding%20from%20Tesco.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20dessert%20of%20choice%20is%20Christmas%20cake%2C%20a%20rich%20fruit%20cake%20covered%20with%20marzipan%20and%20icing.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22christmas%20fruit%20cake%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fc906e950e71a0011558ac9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221755%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristmas%20cake.%3Cp%3Enelea33%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20fruit%20cake%20is%20certainly%20a%20polarizing%20dessert%20wherever%20you%20are%2C%20Brits%20seem%20to%20make%20it%20a%20little%20better%20with%20thick%2C%20sweet%20white%20icing.%C2%A0Oftentimes%2C%20Christmas%20cake%20also%20comes%20topped%20with%20festive%20holly%20decorati