C%20yet%20their%20efforts%20often%20go%20unnoticed.%20By%20placing%20women%E2%80%99s%20names%20on%20doorplates%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20them%20the%20recognition%20and%20dignity%20they%20deserve.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20support%20of%20Paramjit%20Singh%20Bhullar%20and%20a%20few%20other%20women%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EPanchayat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Sheshandeep%20executed%20her%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20confident%20that%20I%20had%20the%20support%20of%20my%20team%2C%20and%20with%20the%20available%20funds%2C%20we%20could%20bring%20my%20plan%20to%20life.%20The%20idea%20of%20adding%20nameplates%20for%20women%20was%20within%20our%20budget.%20So%2C%20we%20swiftly%20moved%20forward%2C%20using%20the%20resources%20already%20allocated%20to%20the%20village.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20around%20110%20households%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Sheshandeep%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20saw%20the%20nameplates%20of%20women%20proudly%20displayed%20on%20every%20door%20in%20the%20village.%20The%20results%20were%20immediate%20and%20impactful.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20one%20young%20woman%20who%20came%20to%20me%2C%20with%20tears%20in%20her%20eyes%2C%20thanking%20me%20for%20this%20initiative.%20She%20said%20she%20had%20never%20been%20allowed%20to%20leave%20her%20home%20or%20make%20decisions%20for%20herself.%20But%20now%2C%20when%20she%20saw%20her%20name%20on%20the%20doorplate%2C%20she%20felt%20proud%20and%20recognised%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheshandeep%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripples%20of%20change%20were%20felt%20across%20the%20village.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20family%2C%20no%20one%20objected%20to%20the%20nameplate.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20my%20name%20is%20recognised%20alongside%20the%20men%E2%80%99s.%20It%20shows%20that%20we%20are%20equal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rani%20Kaur%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20woman%20from%20Manak%20Khana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20see%20my%20name%20