by%20the%20potential%20of%20social%20entrepreneurship%20and%20motivated%20by%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20farmers%20in%20his%20home%20region%2C%20Aman%20took%20a%20significant%20leap.%20He%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20himself%20full-time%20to%20this%20cause%2C%20collaborating%20with%20local%20farmers%20in%20Unnao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMore%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20saw%20businesses%20like%20Phool%2C%20a%20Kanpur-based%20brand%20that%20was%20just%20starting%20out%20at%20the%20time%2C%20doing%20great%20work.%20That%20gave%20me%20the%20confidence%20to%20believe%20that%20if%20someone%20from%20my%20part%20of%20the%20world%20could%20create%20something%20like%20that%2C%20so%20could%20I%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERecognising%20the%20peanut%20crisis%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20an%20internship%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Aman%20had%20gained%20firsthand%20insights%20into%20the%20systemic%20issues%20plaguing%20the%20agricultural%20sector.%20In%20Unnao%2C%20he%20and%20Nutty%20Village%20co-founder%2C%20Sushant%20Berma%2C%20noticed%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20locally%20grown%20peanuts.%20This%20sparked%20their%20curiosity%2C%20leading%20them%20to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20peanut%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20while%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20eating%20peanuts%2C%20we%20started%20talking%20about%20their%20great%20quality.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20out%20and%20do%20some%20research%20to%20see%20what%20was%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sushant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20major%20challenge%20faced%20by%20Unnao%E2%8